      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>tomato paste </strong>in a small bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>tinga paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/944.-step-3-x200.jpg",
