          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1623767915664-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, combine your <strong>mayo </strong>with the juice of <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>lime[s]</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/12 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>lime mayo</strong></p><p>Tip: Roll the lime with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/944.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/944.-step-6-x400.jpg",
