          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Plain-tortillas-on-a-plate-1666709383109-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>chicken tinga</strong>, <strong>grated cheese</strong> and <strong>lime mayo</strong> evenly between the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>tortillas </strong>– these are your <strong>chicken tinga tacos</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
